<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">Another popular "strategy" to this quest is on getting the blood wolf to spawn.  <BR><BR>Drakkel Dire wolves are PH's for the Blood wolf.  You can either quad kite these for exp / faction, or you can do as I did and snare about 13 of these little doggies and bring them over to the coldain huts located just outside of Thurgadin.  The coldain will kill the dire wolves for you, and you can run back and wait for the blood wolf to spawn.  Still seems to take a while to get the blood wolf to spawn, but it's a mana free ( with ES gaunts ) way of clearing the PH's.  <BR><BR>Hope this helps!<BR><BR>_________________<BR>Sareahna Silverwood<BR>51st Wanderer of Bristlebane<BR>Ill Tempered Sea Bass<BR><BR><font size=-1>[ This Message was edited by: Sareahna Silverwood on 2001-06-19 14:30 ]</font></FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#e6ebd7"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=352"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Sareahna Silverwood"></a>
