<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">I have found that if he broodmother is left alone after 1 person loots the leggings.  Fergul will spawn again, and the broodmother will eventually find her way back setting off the script a second, and yes a third time.  I myself looted my leggings off the 3rd spawn.  Took about 3 hours after the 1st spawn for me to do so, but I would recomend that while your looking for your harnes, you may want to try and watch to see if anyone is doing the quest.  Then just hang out near the fort.  If the broodmother finds her way back a 2nd time.  Fergul will spawn.  Free easy way to finnish the quest w/ out doing the quest...  TO bad I did the quest earlier in the day, got trained and the group was killed.  I was in the process of doing it again when I found this out.<BR><BR></FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=613"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of arimus"></a>
